63) Discover a function that takes an array of numbers as input and returns the sum of all the
even numbers in the array.
<?php
function sumEvenNumbers($arr) {
$sum = 0;
foreach ($arr as $num) {
if ($num % 2 == 0) {
$sum += $num;
}
}
return $sum;
}
$numbers = array(1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 10);
echo "Sum of even numbers: " . sumEvenNumbers($numbers);
?>
Output
\Sum of even numbers: 22
